<br>
  In my new guild, a guild with a clue.  There is a paladin in as many groups as possible.  They do clerics are group leaders and grab everyone as they arrive in the zone and do things by different chat channels.  Usually have a MT rotation a CH rotation and a LoH rotation.  Probably 8-10 groups with 4-6 paladins.  If a group ends up with 2 paladins they switch.  At times the paladins are the back up tanks but with usually 6 or so 60 warriors unless its the ring war where you use a FFA type of tactic you dont usually see all the warrior resources overloaded unless its a wipe out.  <br>
<br>
